<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<div type="elementDocumentation" xml:id="elem-source" xmlns:eac="http://archivists.org/ns/eac/v2" xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:ead="https://archivists.org/ns/ead/v4">
               <head>
                  <gi>source</gi>
               </head>
               <div type="fullName">
                  <p>Source</p>
               </div>
               <div type="summary">
                  <p>A required and repeatable child element of <gi>sources</gi> used to identify a particular
                     source of evidence used for the establishment of the descriptive parts in an EAS instance.</p>
               </div>
               <div type="mayContain">
                  <p>citedRange (0..n), descriptiveNote (0..1), objectXMLWrap (0..1), reference (1..n)</p>
               </div>
               <div type="mayOccurWithin">
                  <p>sources</p>
               </div>
               <div type="attributes">
                  <p>
                     <list type="gloss">
                        <label>audience</label>
                        <item>Optional<p type="eac"> (values limited to: external, internal)</p></item>
                        <label>id</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>href</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>languageOfElement</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>linkRole</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>linkTitle</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>scriptOfElement</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>target</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>valueURI</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>vocabularySource</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                        <label>vocabularySourceURI</label>
                        <item>Optional</item>
                     </list>
                  </p>
               </div>
               <div type="description">
                  <p>Use <gi>source</gi> to cite a published resource used in creating the descriptive parts of the EAS instance. Use the required child element <gi>reference</gi>to include a textual identification of the source. In the case of online sources, use <att>href</att> with <gi>reference</gi> to provide a URI.</p>
                  <p>Use the optional child element <gi>citedRange</gi> to point to a specific location within a source.</p>
                  <p>Use the optional <gi>descriptiveNote</gi> for any additional notes about the source. Use the optional <gi>objectXMLWrap</gi> to embed XML documenting the source from any namespace.</p>
                  <p>The prescribed order of all child elements (both required and optional) is:</p>
                  <list type="simple">
                     <item><gi>reference</gi></item>
                     <item><gi>citedRange</gi></item>
                     <item><gi>descriptiveNote</gi></item>
                     <item><gi>objectXMLWrap</gi></item>
                  </list>
               </div>
               <div type="availability">
                  <p>Required, repeatable</p>
               </div>
               <div type="examples">
                  <egXML xml:lang="eng"><![CDATA[<sources>
   <source>
      <reference href="https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gustav_IV._Adolf_(Schweden)">
         Wikipedia
      </reference>
   </source>
   <source>
      <reference href="https://sok.riksarkivet.se/sbl/Presentation.aspx?id=13318">
         Svenskt biografiskt lexikon
      </reference>
      <descriptiveNote>
         <p>
            Stand: 03.12.2020
         </p>
      </descriptiveNote>
   </source>
</sources>]]></egXML>
               </div>
            </div>
